FBIS4-32136 "dreeu119_h_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-119 Daily Report 20 Jun 1994 HUNGARY MSZDP Looking For Left-Wing Cooperation MSZDP Looking For Left-Wing Cooperation LD2006135694 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network in Hungarian 1300 GMT 20 Jun 94 LD2006135694 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network Hungarian BFN [Text] The Social Democratic Party of Hungary [MSZDP] wants to form a cooperation agreement before the local government elections with the Hungarian Socialist Party and the trade unions. The MSZDP's executive authorized the party's Presidium to begin discussions with other left-wing forces which accept the importance of social-democratic ideas in Hungary's political and economic life, the MSZDP's statement says.
